The Best in Des Moines Apartment Living
This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 970 Sq.
The Regatta Apartment Homes are situated in a park-like setting with beautifully landscaped grounds, yet just minutes away from all major services.
We offer well-designed one and two bedroom homes featuring wood burning fireplaces, in-home washer and dryer, wood style flooring and so much more!
Relax in our newly renovated clubhouse and pool or enjoy time on your private patio.
The Regatta is conveniently located less than one mile from the Marina, downtown, light rail and major freeways.
Pricing and availability is subject to change.
Please contact our office for details.
